programme.desc: Ronda Roda kali ini, menampilkan kereta Lexus, Mat Rock Garage dan Yamaha Dragster 650. Yang dihoskan oleh Mira Rizam dengan mempamerkan kereta baru dari Lexus RX dan hasil tangan dari Mat Rock dan Badey Ezam.

programme.title: Durian Oh Durian
programme.desc: Midie seorang posmen, sangat obses untuk melihat pokok durian yang ditanam oleh arwah datuknya sempena kelahirannya berbuah. Tahun demi tahun menanti pokok itu berbuah. Berbagai usaha telah dilakukannya. Walaupun sudah 29 tahun usia pokok itu, namun tidak pernah menunjukkan tanda-tanda akan berbuah, malah pokok tersebut tidak pernah berbunga.

programme.title: Secebis Rindu Ep2
programme.desc: Rasya Aleeya dan Syed Reeza mula berkenalan melalui SMS, membina hubungan cinta walaupun Rasya mengalami paranoia dan Reeza dikenali sebagai lelaki yang suka menggoda. Hubungan mereka diuji apabila Rasya sukar mempercayai Reeza, dipengaruhi masa lalunya dan hasutan Adri, rakan Reeza. Akhirnya, Rasya berkahwin dengan Fahmi, sepupu dan pilihan keluarganya, tetapi perkahwinan itu gagal. Reeza yang terluka terpaksa bertunang dengan Hilda, pilihan keluarganya. Namun, perasaan mereka berdua kembali bercambah selepas bertemu semula di Dubai. Rasya berasa bersalah atas kesilapan lalu tetapi akhirnya mereka berjaya mengatasi salah faham dan ketakutan yang menghalang cinta mereka. Rancangan Reeza untuk menguji perasaan Rasya berjaya memecahkan ego dan ketakutannya. Mereka akhirnya berkahwin dan mendapat restu keluarga, membuktikan cinta sejati mereka mampu bertahan walaupun diuji pelbagai cabaran.

programme.title: Dapur Bujang S17 Ep1

programme.title: Abang Lori Ohsem S1 Ep4
programme.desc: Luqman mencari jalan penyelesaan untuk mencukupkan wang hantarannya serta membantu masalah di kampung dengan berjumpa bapa kandungya Dato Husin. Kedatangan Luqman memang dinanti-nantikan Dato Husin kerana mereka sudah lama terpisah disebabkan Mira yang membenci Dato Husin. Bermulalah Kehidupan Luqman di rumah Dato Husin, namun kehadiran Luqman membuahkan rasa benci ibu tirinya, Datin Ida serta anak-anak Datin Ida, iaitu Dani dan Shaurah. Lufia masih tidak putus asa apabila dia sering menghantui Luqman menagih ganti ruginya, sehingga Luqman terbawak-bawak Lufia di dalam mimpi, tempat kerja dan mana-mana sahaja. Luqman tetap melarikan diri daripada dituntut ganti rugi dengan Lufia. Penipuan Luqman yang kononnya seorang pilot, masih dijalankan sehingga dia sering menyamar jadi pilot di Airport.

programme.title: Paano Ang Pasko (What About Tomorrow) Ep75
programme.desc: Keadaan tidak berjalan lancar untuk Karen. Bukan sahaja Carl terus menolak usahanya untuk mendekati secara romantik, dia juga memutuskan hubungan Karen dengan perniagaannya. Dan lebih teruk lagi, satu pertemuan tegang antara Drake dan Elvira membuatkan Elvira memberitahunya rahsia tentang asal-usul keturunannya.

programme.title: Jendela Hati Ep1
programme.desc: Meskipun Farah sedang menunggu saat diijabkabulkan, namun dia masih dalam dilemma untuk menjadi isteri Lukman. Dia masih keliru dengan keputusannya; antara Amanah arwah Sarah dengan keikhlasannya menerima abang iparnya sebagai suami. Baik Lukman mahupun Farah, kedua-duanya terpaksa maniskan wajah di majlis pernikahan mereka demi menjaga hati Zahin dan kedua-dua orang tua. Di sebalik kegembiraan, ada hati yang tercarik luka dengan pernikahan mereka. Lantaran terlalu kecewa, Myra sanggup bertindak di luar kawalan hingga menyebabkannya kemalangan dan koma. Joshua muncul untuk membantu Myra lalu membawanya ke hospital. Lukman pula resah kerana tidak dapat menjejak Myra setelah Myra hilang begitu sahaja ketika majlis pernikahannya berlangsung. Farah kecewa apabila Lukman berterus terang yang dia takkan menyentuh Farah kerana dia hanya setia dan cintakan arwah isterinya, Sarah.

programme.title: Jendela Hati Ep2

Budi terkejut apabila Lukman datang ke pejabat sehari selepas bernikah seakan-akan mahu mengelak daripada Farah. Lukman terkejut setelah menerima surat perletakan jawatan Myra yang ditinggalkan di atas meja. Papa menegur Lukman yang berperangai seperti orang bujang dan balik lewat meskipun sudah berkahwin. Akibat terasa dengan teguran Papa, Lukman bertindak mengajak Farah balik ke rumahnya. Farah cuba menyesuaikan diri dengan keadaan rumah Lukman yang bersepah dan seakan tidak terurus selepas kematian Sarah. Lukman cemburu dan mula syak wasangka apabila melihat Farah bersama Nazim di kafe.

programme.desc: Sejak pulang ke kampung, Alisya sering diganggu dengan bayangan seorang wanita tua dan kadang-kala dia akan mendengar bunyi buaian yang berayun di luar rumah. Alisya juga sering diganggu dengan mimpi yang bukan-bukan menyebabkan dia terfikir-fikir apa yang sedang terjadi padanya. Suatu malam, usai saja majlis doa selamat di rumah Adnan, Asiah telah melakukan upacara melepaskan sakanya pada Haider. Setelah melepaskan sakanya, wajah Asiah berubah menjadi sangat tua dan badannya membongkok. Asiah hilang jejak selepas itu. Haider tidak menyedari bahawa dirinya kini didampingi oleh saka Asiah dan perangainya mula berubah. Dia menjadi panas-baran, suka makan telur mentah, sentiasa panas dan mula mengsyaki hubungan antara Raden dan Alisya. Raden juga diganggu oleh saka Asiah dengan menjelmakan diri sebagai Alisya. Raden mula tidak sedap hati dan memberitahu hal ini pada Adnan. Raden juga berusaha mencari punca setiap gangguan yang berlaku di rumah tersebut sehingga membawanya ke rumah Asiah. Di situ barulah Raden tahu tentang kisah yang terjadi.

programme.title: Larian Terakhir
programme.desc: Haziq, seorang anak tunggal kepada Mariam yang mempunyai bakat dalam larian pantas, sering berhadapan dengan dugaan kehidupan sehinggakan dia terpaksa meninggalkan ibunya yang sakit. Tanpa disedarinya, pertemuannya dengan Jalal telah memerangkapnya dalam sebuah sindiket jenayah. Walaupun Haziq dijanjikan peluang untuk memperbaiki hidupnya, Amelia sentiasa mengawasi setiap pergerakannya dengan teliti. Larian Terakhir adalah sebuah filem yang menggabungkan genre aksi dan sukan dengan penampilan pelakon-pelakon seperti Fattah Amin, Amyra Rosli, dan Fahrin Ahmad, di mana setiap larian akan sampai ke kemuncaknya.

programme.title: Tom Yum Goong
programme.desc: Seorang pejuang muda bernama Kham mesti pergi ke Australia untuk mendapatkan semula gajah yang dicurinya. Dengan bantuan detektif Australia kelahiran Thailand, Kham mesti menghadapi semua yang datang, termasuk kumpulan yang diketuai oleh seorang wanita jahat dan dua pengawal peribadinya yang maut.

programme.title: Black S1 Ep6
programme.desc: Di Seri Setia, Black dan Sofia bekerjasama untuk menghalang satu pembunuhan yang berpotensi untuk berlaku. Semasa berada di sana, Black terimbas kembali masa lalu Malik, satu fenomena yang membingungkannya. Pemergian mereka ini juga merupakan titik perubahan cara Sofia melihat keupayaannya. Kesanggupan Sofia menggadaikan nyawanya untuk menyelamatkan nyawa orang lain memperbaharui tanggapan Black terhadapnya. Adakah cinta mula berputik? Black tertarik dan pada masa yang sama bingung dengan perasaannya terhadap Sofia, satu perasaan yang asing buat Black, seorang yang mementingkan diri. Tetapi hari yang bersinar menjadi pudar apabila Black kembali ke rumah dan mendapati bilik tersembunyi Malik telah digeledah dan dikosongkan. Sementara itu, pembunuh upahan telah meragut nyawa seorang lagi mangsa dan Detektif Borhan mendapati kematian itu ada kaitan dengan pembunuhan Nurul Najwa.

programme.title: Din Tiger Ep4
programme.desc: Ketegangan meningkat di majlis hari jadi Elyn apabila Din dihina dan dihalau, mengakibatkan konflik yang berterusan berlaku antara ayah dan anak.

programme.title: Plan B Ep8
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Khai meminjam pistol Mika bagi melepaskan geramnya dengan menembak ke beberapa sasaran di tepi pantai. Dia tertekan dengan bapanya, supaya mendalami ilmu agama dan mengaji Al Quran. Kemudian Khai menemui Iris meluahkan perasaannya untuk menjadikan Iris sebagai kekasihnya, sebagai satu alternatif bagi meringankan bebanan fikirannya. Iris seorang gadis kehilangan ayahnya ketika masih kecil. Jadi dia mencari tempat untuk menumpang kasih. Justeru, jika sekiranya Khai membenci ayahnya, bererti dia tidak berkesempatan untuk menumpang kasih. Kesimpulannya, dia juga tidak akan menerima Khai sebagai kekasih tetapi hanya sebagai kawan sahaja.

programme.title: Two Sisters
programme.desc: Selepas seorang gadis dibebaskan dari rumah sakit jiwa, dia disatukan semula dengan kakaknya dan mereka kembali ke rumah keluarga yang ditinggalkan. Namun, kedua-dua beradik itu menyimpan rahsia gelap dan tragis keluarga yang mula terungkap selepas kepulangan mereka.

programme.title: Binhi
programme.desc: Daniel dan Cynthia, pasangan muda dengan anak dalam perjalanan, mengalami masa sukar di Manila. Mereka kembali ke Baguio, tempat asal Daniel, untuk memulakan semula. Melalui kebaikan Alex, kawan Daniel zaman kanak-kanak yang kaya, mereka dapat tinggal di sebuah rumah besar, tanpa sewa; dan dia mendapat tawaran kerja juga. Segala-galanya seolah-olah jatuh pada tempatnya untuk mereka - atau begitulah yang mereka fikirkan - sehingga perkara aneh mula berlaku di rumah mereka.

programme.title: Ong Bak 3
programme.desc: Kisah pahlawan Tien, yang telah ditangkap oleh panglima perang yang kejam Tuan Rajasena. Tien melarikan diri daripada cengkaman Rajasena, pulih daripada kecederaannya yang melumpuhkan dengan bantuan Guru Bua, dan kembali untuk berhadapan dengan Bhuti Sangkha, yang telah menggantikan Rajasena sebagai penjahat utama.

programme.title: Takut Ke Tak
programme.desc: Lima pelajar jurusan filem merancang untuk melakukan penggambaran di sebuah rumah berhantu, namun satu demi satu kejadian yang sama seperti kebanyakan filem seram berlaku kepada mereka lalu mereka perlu membuat keputusan penting takut ke tak?

programme.title: Bodyguard
programme.desc: Seorang lelaki yang kehilangan cinta dan keinginannya untuk hidup bekerja bersama rakan-rakan zaman kanak-kanaknya di sebuah syarikat pinjaman persendirian. Suatu hari, dia bertemu dengan seorang wanita yang sedang dikejar oleh penyerang yang tidak dikenali. Wanita itu merupakan satu-satunya pewaris kepada sebuah korporat. Dia sedang diburu oleh seseorang yang cuba merampas syarikat tersebut. Sementara itu, pemilik syarikat pinjaman tersebut mula mencari wanita itu.

programme.title: The Hollow One
programme.desc: Rachel dan Anna pulang ke rumah dua tahun selepas kematian ibu mereka, dan dapati bandar itu ditinggalkan dengan rumah mereka dalam keadaan kacau dan kotor. Apabila Rachel mula mengalami halusinasi mengenai ibu mereka yang sudah meninggal dan sesuatu artifak purba, petunjuk-petunjuk menakutkan mula terbongkar mengenai masa lalu keluarga mereka.

programme.title: On Halloween
programme.desc: Satu siri kematian dan kehilangan kejam membawa kembali kepada legenda bandar tentang badut pembunuh bersiri. Sekumpulan pelajar kolej akan menghadapi mimpi ngeri terburuk mereka, apabila Badut jahat ini kembali dari masa lalu pada Halloween.

programme.title: Minyak Dagu
programme.desc: Minyak Dagu mengisahkan tentang Azman yang berdendam dengan bekas tunangnya Emelda dan disebabkan terlalu dendam dan mengikut pujukan daripada kawannya, Azman telah berjumpa bomoh, Wak Minarjo seorang pawang hebat minyak dagu. Emelda yang memutuskan pertunangan dengan Azman demi mengikut cakap kedua-dua orang tuanya bahawa Johan adalah seorang calon suami yang baik dan boleh menjamin masa depan Emelda, nak dibandingkan Azman yang hanya seorang jurujual yang sering tak ada untungnya.

programme.title: Plan B Ep12
programme.desc: Mengisahkan pasukan polis mengepung premis awam di mana Khai dan Iris bersembunyi dan menculik beberapa perkerja sebagai tebusan. Sebelum ini Mika yang cedera di dada akibat ditembak polis turut berada dalam premis itu. Que dibawa oleh Inspektor Faris untuk berunding dengan Khai supaya membebaskan tebusan. Khai hanya membebaskan dua tebusan setelah syarat menyerahkan Que kepadanya dipenuhi. Kedua-dua ibu bapa Khai dan Mika turut berada di tempat kejadian itu. Setelah mengubah aliran CCTV, beberapa anggota polis berjaya merempuh masuk ke premis itu. Khai, Iris, Que dan Mika diberkas polis.

Uzair terkejut apabila Hatta datang berlawan dengannya menentang Imran. Mereka cuba melarikan diri dari bandar tetapi Imran menggunakan Ajeeb mempunyai umpan.

programme.title: Karantina
programme.desc: 5 pelajar pergi ke lawatan sekolah di Pulau Karantina untuk kelas Sejarah. Tetapi salah seorang daripada mereka akan tersesat ke hospital terbiar dan rakan sekelasnya perlu mencarinya, menghadapi ancaman paranormal di sepanjang jalan.

Apabila kerajaan Thai mengumumkan rancangan untuk mengosongkan bilik kebalnya untuk membayar balik pinjaman IMFnya, sekumpulan Mafia tempatan membuat satu skim untuk rompakan mega, mereka akan mencuri rizab emas negara. Mereka mengupah Navin yang terkenal, bekas pembunuh tentera, untuk mengetuai operasi yang melibatkan semua pencuri terkemuka di negara ini.

programme.title: Kapsul
programme.desc: Kapsul masa wawasan 2020 yang ditanam oleh Tun Dr. Mahathir Mohamad telah dicuri dan membawa Zohri kembali ke masa lalu. Zohri kini terperangkap di tengah-tengah pergolakan bangsa Melayu untuk mencapai kemerdekaan dan membawa bangsa Melayu keluar dari belenggu kemiskinan. Zohri melihat dan merasai sendiri erti perjuangan umatnya yang tidak pernah dibayangkannya selama ini. Dia lihat, dia rasa dan kini dia mula faham betapa peritnya liku-liku sejarah negara dan bangsa. Perjalanan Zohri berterusan dari satu zaman ke satu zaman dan tiada siapa yang dapat mengembalikannya ke zamannya melainkan dirinya sendiri.

programme.desc: Sekumpulan orang dewasa muda dihantar ke planet yang jauh untuk bersaing dalam permainan Sol Invictus yang berprestij.

programme.title: Gemersik Berbisik Ep5
programme.desc: Kimi dan Tasya ikut Daniel serta Suhana melawat kubur Suzana. Tasya dirasuk semasa perjalanan balik dan menyanyikan lagu Tepukamai-amai tiba-tiba.

programme.title: Mantera Anjasmoro Ep1
programme.desc: Episod ini mengisahkan pasangan suami dan isteri, Zahid dan Sabrina, masih belum mempunyai anak kerana kehamilan Sabrina telah beberapa kali gugur. Kini, Sabrina mengalami ketekanan dan sering mimpi ngeri serta diganggu oleh bunyi yang ganjil. Zahid berasa bosan dengan Sabrina kerana selalu menceritakan mimpi ngeri. Tanpa diketahui Sabrina, Zahid dan Suria, seorang rakan Sabrina, telah menjalinkan perhubungan sulit.

programme.title: Mantera Anjasmoro Ep2
programme.desc: Episod ini mengisahkan Zahid dan Suria bernikah tanpa pengetahuan Sabrina, dan mereka merahsiakan perkara tersebut. Tiba-tiba, Sabrina pula menyampaikan berita gembira yang dia telah dua bulan mengandung. Walaupun Zahid berasa gembira akan menjadi seorang ayah, berita itu amat menyedihkan Suria. Lalu, Suria berjumpa seorang bomoh untuk mendapatkan petua untuk mengikat hati Zahid dan memastikan kandungan Sabrina gugur.

programme.title: Mantera Anjasmoro Ep3
programme.desc: Episod ini mengisahkan Sabrina mengesyaki sesuatu yang tidak kena setelah terbaca passport Zahid yang menunjukkan dia berada di sebelah sempadan, dan pada masa sama Suria pula bercuti. Sabrina mengambil keputusan berjumpa Ramona, seorang bomoh, yang mengesahkan Zahid dan Suria baru bernikah. Sabrina meminta pertolongan bomoh itu untuk memastikan perhubungan Zahid dan Suria putus, serta menjamin kandungnya selamat. Pada masa sama, Suria meminta bomohnya memastikan dia memikat hati Zahid, dan Zahid benci Sabrina.

programme.title: Mantera Anjasmoro Ep4
programme.desc: Episod ini mengisahkan Sabrina menggunakan minyak jampi dan membaca mantera, mengakibatkan Zahid mengaku dia dan Suria telah bernikah. Sabrina sukar menerima pengakuan Zahid dan hendak berpisah dengan Zahid. Suria berasa gembira berkelakuan Sabrina, namun bomoh Ramona menasihatkan Sabrina pulang ke rumah serta terus menggunakan minyak jampi dan membaca mantera. Sementara itu, apabila Suria pergi rumah bomoh Din untuk mendapatkan lebih banyak petua, anak Din mengatakan bapanya sudah meninggal dunia dua tahun dahulu. Berita itu mengejutkan Suria dan dia tidak tenang. Seterusnya, doktor mengesan Suria telah mengandung dua bulan

programme.title: Barajiwa Ep8
programme.desc: Imran membunuh Ajeeb dan Uzair bersumpah untuk membalas dendam. Tanpa berfikir panjang Hatta mahu segera menyerang Imran tetapi Uzair mahu memastikan rakan-rakannya selamat. Ashikin merayu agar Imran menghentikan dendamnya terhadap Uzair. Apabila Imran menculik Noramina, bermulalah pertarungan terakhir.

programme.title: Black Demon
programme.desc: Percutian keluarga berubah menjadi mimpi ngeri apabila mereka berdepan dengan seekor jerung megalodon ganas. Terdampar dan diserang tanpa henti, Paul dan keluarganya mesti mencari jalan untuk kembali ke pantai dengan selamat sebelum jerung itu menyerang lagi.

programme.title: Ali Setan
programme.desc: Ali pelajar universiti yang nakal dan suka bergurau berjumpa Asmidar ketika dalam perjalanan ke universiti. Ali selalu mencari jalan untuk mengusik Asmidar, lama kelamaan perasaan cinta mula berputik antara mereka berdua. Konflik mula terjadi apabila Ali sebenarnya sudah berkahwin dengan Tipah namun atas sebab terpaksa.

programme.title: Cinta U-Turn
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Faiz, seorang anak lelaki kepada ahli perniagaan bernama Datuk Shuib yang ingin dijodohkan dengan Juliana. Kekeliruan mula berlaku apabila gambar Juliana telah bertukar dengan gambar orang lain yang tidak menepati citrasa Faiz. Dia melarikan diri dan berkenalan dengan Hafiz. Mereka bersama-sama bekerja di sebuah bengkel. Pada suatu hari, Juliana datang ke bengkel itu dan telah membuatkan Faiz jatuh cinta padanya. Keadaan menjadi huru hara apabila berlakunya penyamaran antara Faiz dan Hafiz dalam memenangi hati bapa Juliana, iaitu Datuk Jamal.

programme.title: Ali Setan 2
programme.desc: Ikatan yang ingin tercipta terpaksa dileraikan kerana campur tangan keluarga menyebabkan Ali dan Asmidar pergi membawa haluan sendiri. Rancangan untuk mendirikan rumahtangga telah diganggu oleh Jeff yang inginkan Asmidar. Ayah Asmidar pula menyuruhnya berkahwin bersama Jeff - namun setelah beberapa bulan mereka pun bercerai kerana tidak bahagia. Ali dan Asmidar pun bersatu semula.

programme.title: Bila Dah Sayang
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Kamarudin yang tak jadi bertunang dengan Tengku Suraya kerana kekasihnya itu masih belum bersedia untuk berkahwin. Dalam hati mereka masih ada perasaan sayang antara satu sama lain walaupun mereka sering bertengkar. Namun berlaku satu insiden yang membuatkan Kamarudin terpikat dengan seorang gadis Cina bernama Miss Yap.

programme.title: Puteri Impian
programme.desc: Pekerja kilang, Puteri Nora sentiasa mengimpikan untuk menjadi seorang puteri raja. Impiannya menjadi kenyataan apabila dia diterima menyertai pertandingan "Memburu Impian". Kehidupannya berubah sekelip mata apabila bertemu Tengku Faizal, seorang putera raja. Namun, Zul, jurukameranya dalam rancangan itu turut menyukai Puteri Nora. Pilihan harus dibuat antara kemewahan atau kebebasan.

programme.title: Cinta Bollywood
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Shahrul, anak Tok Penghulu merangkap seorang penganggur yang tinggal di Parit Buntar bersama keluarganya. Dia menaruh hati kepada seorang gadis bernama Asha. Pada suatu hari, seorang penerbit filem telah datang ke kampungnya untuk membuat penggambaran drama berjudul Cinta Bollywood. Shahrul kemudiannya dilantik menjadi production manager dan pelakon untuk penggambaran drama itu. Ketika penggambaran dibuat, Salman, hero drama itu semakin rapat dengan Asha dan hal ini membuatkan Shahrul cemburu.

programme.title: Puteri Impian 2
programme.desc: Gadis kilang yang menolak lamaran seorang kerabat diraja Tengku Faizal, menaruh hati terhadap jurukamera stesen televisyen, Zul. Nora menyukai Zul tetapi dia telah pun menjalin hubungan bersama Lisa. Adik kepada Tengku Faizal, Tengku Farid ingin membawa semula Nora kembali ke abangnya. Tekad, dia ingin mengangkat semula maruah abangnya.

programme.title: Cikgu Romantik
programme.desc: Bercita-cita ingin menjadi selebriti terkenal, Azizah mendapat surat uji bakat yang bertempat di Kuala Lumpur. Dia pun pergi dan menetap di rumah temannya, Tila lalu berkenalan bersama seorang guru vokal iaitu Ramli. Muncul pula Shahrul yang mengatakan bahawa raut wajah Azizah seiras dengan isterinya yang telah meninggal dunia.

programme.title: Nylea & Harris

programme.title: The Borderless World (M) Ep759
programme.desc: Journalist with an infallible nose for a story is leading the audience to explore the world. Exploring how people from different cultures overcome the challenges with collective wisdom.

programme.title: Mr.Player (M) Ep533
programme.desc: Depending on the locations of the missions, Jacky Wu, the leader of the home team, invites various celebrities to take on challenges and bring you excitement every week.

programme.title: Gung Hay Fat Choy (M) Ep38
programme.desc: In a bad economy, many people dream of becoming rich overnight, especially the Jiang family. Mother Jiang pushes her three children to earn money so that they can one day live in luxury. Even her daughter-in-law wishes for the same thing. She hopes that one day she can visit her parents with the money that spills out of her purse.

programme.title: The Eagle Shooting Heroes
programme.desc: Executive produced by Wong Kar Wai, The Eagle Shooting Heroes is loosely based on Louis Chas classics. Whilst mistaken identity and rampant gender confusion are on the menu, Sammo Hungs action direction and the incredible all-star casts also keep the laughs and thrills coming in this Hong Kong-style crazy comedy.

programme.title: Everything Under Control
programme.desc: During a diamond heist, one of the security escorts, Jelly, steals the diamonds and flees. Fellow security escorts, Yau Shing and Penguin, are forced to help the robber track down the diamonds. They stumble onto a remote village along the way, encountering strange villagers and mysterious incidents. Can they finally locate Jelly and the diamonds?

programme.title: Marriage With A Liar
programme.desc: Kiki and her boyfriend of seven years, Sean, are to be married in a week but both cheated on each other three days before the wedding. Faced with each of their perfect partners, Kiki and Sean ignore their responsibilities to each other and choose to go their separate ways

programme.title: Article 20
programme.desc: Han Ming, a prosecutor, faces a whirlwind of complications in his work and family lives: his son's clash with another student in school and his wife's intervention, as well as the strained partnerships at work. Amidst it all, a critical case challenges his sense of righteousness, and he decides to gamble everything to seek fairness and justice.

programme.title: Crypto Storm
programme.desc: ICAC investigation officer Lok sets up a special team to investigate a corruption case involving a banks top executives use of cryptocurrency to manipulate the trading market. When the banks chairman is kidnapped and kidnappers demand ransom in crypto coins, Lok connects the dots and vows to hunt down the mastermind behind both crimes.

programme.title: 72 Tenants of Prosperity
programme.desc: Ha Kung and Shek Kin are sworn brothers, but become sworn enemies in business and every aspect of life after Pinky, the girl they love, marries Ha Kung. It is only when the property owner of both their shops wants to terminate their tenancies forty years later, that they are able to resolve the rivalry.

programme.title: Invisible Target
programme.desc: Three young police officers driven by different motives decide to join forces to defeat Tien and his lethal, mercenary gang. As they team up to prevent another massive robbery, they discover that it is instigated by another unknown man. With courage, wits and dexterity, the trio are determined to not let Tien and the instigator escape.

programme.title: Beyond the Dream
programme.desc: Primary school teacher Lok is a recovering schizophrenic who falls in love with a young girl he first met. As he struggles to reveal his illness, Lok has a relapse and becomes delusional. Little does he know she is a mental health counsellor who has a hidden agenda. The pair develops a relationship that is beyond their wildest dreams.

programme.title: See You Tomorrow
programme.desc: In this chaotic world, every city has its own "navigators" who can help solve various relationship issues. Bar owner Chen and his partner Guan are legendary navigators, but in the process of helping a girl Xiao Yu, they must also face their own problems in an epic act of self-discovery that brings their lives from towering highs to withering lows.

programme.title: Tainted Love
programme.desc: Office lady Zhou Ran falls victim to an online dating love scam and is cheated of 550,000 yuan. Following faint clues left by the scammer, Zhou Ran comes to a small coastal town and encounters two young men. She gradually discovers that these two men have hidden the clues of the scam, and sets out on her revenge plan.

programme.title: Wo Hu
programme.desc: The Hong Kong Police has placed more than a thousand undercover officers in various triad groups to bring down the largest criminal organization in Hong Kong. Betrayal, deceit and murder bring this group of "brothers" into a collision with the law and with each other!

programme.title: Midnight Fly
programme.desc: With her marriage in crisis, Michele takes off to Europe for a vacation and meets a Japanese woman named Miki. As they become friends and travel together, Michele discovers that Miki is her husband's mistress. When Miki goes missing in Morocco, Michele does everything she can to find her but ends up paying a heavy price

programme.title: I Love Hong Kong
programme.desc: Ng Shun and his family return to the public housing estate where he grew up, not to visit his aging father, but to seek refuge after his business has failed. When his family of five squeeze into the small estate unit, Ng Shun is forced to face his long-neglected family problems...

programme.title: Heroic Duo
programme.desc: Police officer Ken needs help to solve a grisly crime that the offender has no recollection of committing. Ken seeks out Jack, a former psychologist who is now imprisoned. Forming an uneasy truce, this unconventional duo sets out to find the man responsible. It is at this time that Ken falls into a trap set up by Jack

programme.title: Bodyguards and Assassins
programme.desc: On 15 October 1906, Chinese revolutionary leader Sun Yat Sen returned to Hong Kong to stage another overthrow of the Qing dynasty. Businessman Lee and Chinese Dailys Chief Chan arrange for five bodyguards to protect Mr Sun - these are all extraordinary fighters who are ready and up for fierce battles against the Qing assassination army.

programme.title: Initial D
programme.desc: The movie is adapted from a famous Japanese manga. 18-year-old Takumi delivers tofu in his father's near-obsolete car every day and becomes a good racer with perfect drifting skill. Encouraged by his father, he joins a mountain race and unexpectedly wins it, making him famous overnight and leading him from one exciting race to another.

programme.title: I'm Livin' It
programme.desc: Once a successful banker, Bowen now spends his nights in a 24-hour fast food joint where he meets a group of homeless people. Together they strive to get themselves out of rock bottom.

programme.title: Moscow Mission
programme.desc: Based on the 1993 true event of the "China-Russia Train Robbery", a gang of criminals commits a heist, stealing cash and goods from the cross border train. A Chinese police officer disguises as a businessman takes charge of the operation to arrest the criminals, but uncovers a bigger conspiracy instead

programme.title: Table for Six 2
programme.desc: The sequel to "Table for Six", Bernard and Lung plan to get married while their eldest brother is away. Yet, the weddings spiral into a chaotic battleground with escalating family drama, creating a messy affair for everyone involved.

programme.title: Wolf Hiding
programme.desc: A cold-blooded killer, Chen An vows to take revenge for her sister who was killed by a crime gang. Dealing with the police and the triad at the same time, a final battle between good and evil has just begun!

programme.title: Tristar
programme.desc: Young priest Hong disguises himself to protect Bai, a prostitute, while Detective Liu investigates her ties to a prostitution ring. Hong finds Bai a lawful job and helps her negotiate with the underworld. Meanwhile, Liu's investigation causes misunderstandings can he crack down on the gang? How will Hong manage his emotions as Bai falls for him?

programme.title: Hello Stranger
programme.desc: This is a Thai romantic comedy. The story portrays a young Thai man and woman who meet by coincidence while on vacation in South Korea. They decide to tour the country together while keeping their names a secret from each other. From unwillingly at first, then become best friends and fall in love finally.

programme.title: Chinese Odyssey 2002
programme.desc: Set in Ming Dynasty, young Emperor Zheng De escapes from the palace with his sister who disguised as a man. They run into a notorious wanderer who runs a restaurant with his boyish sister in Jiang Nan. The two pairs of siblings from vastly different social classes descend into an inescapable swirl of gender confusion, slapstick antics and love.

programme.title: Death Stranding
programme.desc: To overhaul the underground gambling industry, the police join hands with the gambling association to crack down on illegal casinos. They auction off new casino licenses to regulate the industry, but this results in an upheaval in the gambling world, unveiling the hidden interests and secrets while sparking conflicts between gangs...

programme.title: Fagara
programme.desc: After her fathers death, a Hong Kong girl discovers she has two hitherto unknown sisters, Branch and Cherry. Through taking up her late fathers hotpot restaurant, she reunites with her sisters by different mothers, and understands her father more from a different perspective, allowing her to finally resolve her long-time hard feelings with him.

programme.title: The Lost Bladesman
programme.desc: An epic historic adventure set during the turbulent times of the Three Kingdoms. Cao Cao attempts to enlist Guan Yu into his forces, but Guan is loyal to his sworn brother Liu Bei, who is also Caos enemy. As Guan tries to rescue Liu Beis concubine from Cao, he is forced to fight his way through. Can he succeed in the end?

programme.title: Bounty Hunters
programme.desc: A group of bounty hunters, including San, Yo, Cat, Swan and Bobo, are tasked to track down the culprit of a series of bombings that have plagued an international hotel group. Unfortunately, Swan, Cat and Bobo are kidnapped by the mastermind of the bombings. Can San and Yo save them? Will the bounty hunters accomplish their mission?

programme.title: All U Need is Love
programme.desc: Ten major film companies join forces on a comedy-drama film to raise funds and create jobs for industry workers during the COVID-19 pandemic. This film features an all-star ensemble cast starring for free, with the story revolving around a group of hotel guests placed under quarantine in Hong Kong.

programme.title: A Legend
programme.desc: Archaeologist Professor Fang uncovers artifacts from a glacier expedition that resembles a jade pendant in his dream. To unveil the truth, Professor Fang leads his team to a journey into the glacier, embarking on a fantastical adventure together.

programme.title: The Fierce Wife
programme.desc: An Zhen divorces her husband after his infidelity but faces a pivotal decision four years later - to return to her cheating husband and old life or to embark on a new life with a new love?

programme.title: A Maid From Heaven
programme.desc: The seventh daughter of the Jade Emperor is banished from heaven to live a mortal life as she is very mischievous. She falls in love with a young village lad Yong, who sold himself to work for the rich so as to bury his father. The goddess sisters help Yong to pay his debt so the lovebirds can be together. Is this going to end happily-ever-after?

programme.title: Clan Feuds
programme.desc: Like legendary director Chu Yuan did so often and so successfully, Chang Peng Yi adapted this film from a story by Ku Lung. Following the footsteps of the equally legendary Chang Cheh, Chang also casted the majestic Ti Lung, along with "Venoms Lo Meng and Sun Chien, for a spectacular showcase of mystical Martial Arts Worlds intrigue and consummate Kung Fu.

programme.title: Tiger Killer
programme.desc: Wu Song is appointed as chief constable after killing a tiger with his bare hands when drunk. The wife of his brother Wu Da Lang, seduces Wu Song but gets rejected by him, and engages in an affair with a rich man. They poison Wu Da Lang when he finds out about their affair. To avenge his brothers death, Wu Song kills both of them.

programme.title: Finger of Doom
programme.desc: The protagonists are ex-swordmasters who now find joy in making umbrellas. They track down the evil Madame Kung Sun and her poisonous Finger of Doom, a unique supernatural power which allows her to transform normal, everyday people into horrifying zombies, and this is just the start of their mythical adventure against this zombie maker!

programme.title: The Dancing Millionairess
programme.desc: Peter was a key dancer in a dance troupe and applied to be the chauffeur of a rich girl, Betty. When he is rumoured to be her lover, Betty is furious and goes undercover as a reporter to investigate the rumour. They fall in love in the process, and after putting Peter through many tests, they finally seal their love with a dance.

programme.title: What Price Honesty
programme.desc: In this period martial arts thriller, three police graduates are assigned to a town rife with crimes and corruption. They vow to uphold justice but are hampered by their corrupt superior, resulting in them putting their lives and the lives of their beloved in danger.

programme.title: Between Tears and Smiles
programme.desc: Fan Jia Shu is a kind-hearted student who is smitten with Shen, a heart-rending love song singer. However, he is not the only one who has eyes for Shen. The Generals henchmen are also determined to present the songstress to their superior as a gift. Fan receives help from an unexpected person just in time to save the woman he loves.

programme.title: The Golden Buddha
programme.desc: A map indicating the location of the Chans family heirloom is hidden in three Golden Buddha statues. Paul, an insurance agent, finds one statue by chance and Chans daughter has another one. This makes them targets of treasure-hunting criminals and they have to team up to defeat them before unveiling the hidden secrets.

programme.title: The Tigress Of Shaolin
programme.desc: Sam is being hunted as he discovers that the mayor and the chief of medical bureau are colluding with a drug dealer. He is saved by a fishermen family and works in their friends grocery but the grocery owner is killed when the enemies track Sam down. Sam escapes to Shaolin to learn the cudgel style of kung fu in order to avenge his friends.

programme.title: The Master Of Kung Fu
programme.desc: The famous kung fu master Wong Fei Hung teaches martial arts in Guangdong. A vicious gangster plots to harm Wongs disciples and frames him for robbery and murder. Wong has to fight against the culprit to prove his own innocence and take revenge for his disciples.

programme.title: Three Sinners
programme.desc: Based on the classic Ming Dynasty novel The Water Margin, Three Sinners is a Huangmei Opera about love, betrayal, murder, and redemption. Starring Hong Kong's premiere movie couple, it is one of the grandest Eastmancolor-Shawscope costume musicals in the Shaw Brothers library.

programme.title: Rivals of Kung Fu
programme.desc: Shen and Wong Fei Hungs relationship turns sour, and Shen frames Wong and his disciple for murder. They are saved by a businessman Zhou, but Wong must win the Lion Dance Trophy to return Zhous favour. Can Wong Fei Hung defeat all skilled martial artists and complete his mission?

programme.title: The Heroic Ones
programme.desc: The story is set in the Tang Dynasty and David Chiang plays the 13th Prince, a powerful fighter whose prestigious status provokes jealously, leading to a gruesome family feud.

programme.title: Shaolin Prince
programme.desc: As the names of Chang Cheh and Liu Chia-liang became legendary, all-too-often the name of their equally valued collaborator, Tang Chia, is omitted. That may be, because, unlike the previous pair, the veteran kung-fu choreographer only went on to direct three movies of his own. Of course, that makes this trio all the more special, and this first effort perhaps the most special of all. It may be an eye-filling, mind-bending martial arts tale of two royal princes battling for the rightful recovery of the throne, but it's also a party, where Tang invites two cinematographers, three editors, and no less than five other choreographer friends to almost literally shoot the works. The results are kung-fu configurations not only never seen before, but never even imagined!

programme.title: Love without End
programme.desc: Singer Qing Qing and architect Peng Nan are a devoted couple. Qing Qing sacrifices herself to help Peng Nan when his family is going through difficulties and is misunderstood by Peng Nan, leading to their break up. When Peng Nan learns the truth and decides to make up with Qing Qing, he finds out that she is suffering from a terminal illness.

programme.title: Invincible Enforcer
programme.desc: A young man is at the wrong place at the wrong time. As he offends a police inspector, he is thrown into jail and even when released, the police goes after him until he has no choice but to become a real criminal. Only a kind and beautiful probation officer is on his side, but can she help him?

programme.title: Mr Funny - bone
programme.desc: Join Mr Funny bone in a series of comic vignettes as he attempts to win the heart of a dashing lady. Along for the ride is his loyal sidekick Mr Big Potato, a stout fellow who is forever getting into silly mishaps. The pair gets involved in plenty of shenanigans and gags!

programme.title: The Five Venoms
programme.desc: A dying master dispatches his last pupil to track down five ex-students who are each an expert in his own lethal combat style. He fears they will steal the fortune belonging to their clan and tasks his pupil to prevent their attempt.

programme.title: Lover's Rock
programme.desc: Pan Lei, winner the China Literary Award for three consecutive years, wrote and directed this film about the lives and loves of a fishing village. It starred the glorious Cheng Pei-pei in her first film as a woman (she had debuted in a mans role), and her much-lauded performance won her the prestigious Golden Accolade Award from the International Association Of Independent Producers a first for any Asian woman.

programme.title: Demon of the Lute
programme.desc: Lute demon Chin Mo has reappeared in the world to wreak havoc. Hsiao Feng Ling is ordered to help find a special bow and arrows that can counter the demon. Only Chiao Yin knows the whereabouts of the weapon. Hsiao and her classmate Old Naughty set out on an arduous journey to find Chiao. After overcoming many obstacles, they catch Chin Mo's man trying to snatch the bow and manage to stop him in time....

programme.title: Killer Darts
programme.desc: A group of bandits raided the village where dart master Liu lives and killed his wife. While hunting them down, Lius disciple kills a farmer and his wife when she refuses his advances, leading Liu to adopt their orphaned daughter and raises her with his son. Years later, the daughter meets a man with the bandits and is tricked to go against Liu.

programme.title: The Delinquent
programme.desc: This is a coming-of-age tale depicting the lower class Hong Kong troubled youths in the 1960s and the societal issues that they face. Wang Chung is a hotheaded and rebellious teen who is tempted by the dark side, and have to unfortunately pay a huge price for it.

programme.title: Heaven Sword and Dragon Sabre
programme.desc: In the Yuan Dynasty, martial artists everywhere battle for the Heaven Sword and the Dragon Sabre, as only when these two powerful weapons combine can a secret be revealed to help one become the king of the martial arts world. As Zhang Wu Ji acquires the skills from Nine Yang Scriptures by chance, he is also embroiled in this lengthy battle.

programme.title: The Happiest Moment
programme.desc: This erotic comedy anthology features three stories about an old man who dies from an overdose of virility pills, a cop who goes on the run after extorting money from a hooker, and a barber's apprentice who encounters a lively corpse in a night vigil. Through playing all these characters, Michael Hui proves himself as a genius of Hong Kong comedy.

programme.title: The Shepherd Girl
programme.desc: In this musical drama, Hsiu Hsiu, a beautiful shepherd girl, falls in love with a handsome boatman Ta Lung. However, she cannot afford to marry him because of her fathers towering debt from gambling. To complicate the matter, a rival suitor promises to pay off all her father's debts on one condition: that Hsiu Hsiu marries him...

programme.title: The House of 72 Tenants
programme.desc: The 72 inhabitants of a dilapidated tenement live under the thumb of a heartless landlady and her sleazy husband. The arrival of a defiant new tenant however, changes their fate. The residents pool their resources together to prevent evictions, deflect targeted harassment by a corrupt policeman and ultimately prevent their home from being sold.

programme.title: Tales of a Eunuch
programme.desc: Tales Of A Eunuch reunites the potent mix of martial arts superstar Gordon Liu, who plays Emperor in cognito Kang Hsi, with the kung-fu comedienne Wang Yu, an anti-Ching revolutionary. It is a film laced with wild barrages of excellent martial arts chiefly choreographed by Yuen Hua and Yuan Pien; Jackie Chan's long-time kung-fu classmates. At one time, Wang was considered to be the next Alexander Fu Sheng.

programme.title: Sex, Love and Hate
programme.desc: This masterpiece spins three interconnected tales about Hong Kong society's differing views on love and what women want from love. Follow a trio of Hong Kong women as they explore relationships and fulfil their hopes of finding true love.

programme.title: The Fake Ghost Catchers
programme.desc: Huan Zhu's ghost seeks help from Fake Ghost Catchers Bao Tuo and Zhou Peng, after a jealous suitor's ghost seeks vengeance by murdering her and now targeting her sister. Together with actor Wu Shun Chao who possesses a supernatural talent, they unite to protect Huan Zhu's sister from both mortal and spectral threats.

programme.title: River of Tears
programme.desc: Retired singer Fang lives happily with her husband and son. Tragedy happens when a man from her past returns to haunt her. In an ensuing struggle to free her from his clutches, her husband dies in a car accident. Blamed by her father-in-law for her husbands death, Fang gets chased out of the house and goes back to singing to make a living...

programme.title: Killers Five
programme.desc: The Dukes daughter has been kidnapped by the notorious Golden Dragon Hill bandits. A swordman named Yue Zhen Bei is assigned to save her, and expecting many dangers on the journey, Yue garners help from a group of good friends who are also kung fu masters.

programme.title: The Bride Napping
programme.desc: A rich girl Yue Ying, together with her maid Chun Lan, encounter a poor scholar Bian Ji at a fte. Chun Lan realizes Yue Ying is in love with him, but mixes his identity with a bandit due to an old servants confusion, threatening the couples union. After a series of complications, misunderstandings and mismatches, Chun Lan finally saves the day.

programme.title: Temple Of The Red Lotus
programme.desc: A young guy Wu, heads off to the Dragon Valley to meet his childhood friend Lian Chu, who was promised to be his bride. When he arrives, he finds out that the family of his bride may not be an entirely honest bunch of people. Wu wishes to take Lian Chu with him, so he has no choice but to fight against her family

programme.title: My Dream Boat
programme.desc: This is a story about the complicated love relationships between a group of young friends who are entangled in a web of love and emotions.

programme.title: Go, Dog. Go! Ep10
programme.desc: All Paws on Deck / Bonestand and Deliver - Tag wants to do something special for her Mom and Paws anniversary, so she recreates the boat cruise where her parents first met. \ Tag discovers that nothing is planned for Pawstons 100th birthday, so she decides the town needs to rebuild the old Bonestand for a big Pawston concert.

programme.title: Trolls: The Beat Goes On! Ep13
programme.desc: Model Behavior / Pillow Fight Club - Satin and Chenille put on a fashion show to impress the trendsetter of Troll VillagePoppy and Branch start a massive villagewide pillow battle to determine who gets the pillow of destiny.

programme.title: Trolls: The Beat Goes On! Ep14
programme.desc: The Imposter / Frenemy - When there is an imposter in Troll Village, Branch and Poppy embark on a man-hunt as to try to keep the Trolls from realizing that anything is off/Poppy discovers that Archer Pastry belongs to a group of evil creatures called the Party Crashers

programme.title: All Hail King Julien: Exiled Ep65

programme.title: All Hail King Julien Ep66

programme.title: The Epic Tales of Captain Underpants Ep37
programme.desc: Captain Underpants and the Ludicrous Lunacy of the Loopy Laserlightmare - Despite being terrible at the job, Krupp wants to be the camp director again next summer. That's something Harold and George simply cannot abide.

programme.title: The Epic Tales of Captain Underpants Ep38
programme.desc: Captain Underpants and the Shocking Showdown of the Staggering Sugamechangere - It's parents' weekend at Lake Summer Camp, and Krupp's eager to make amends with Harold and George ... or so he says.
